narratives.question_text: Were the resources available to you - library, fabrication labs, classroom, software, desk space, etc. adequate for the fulfillment of the assigned work?  If not, please make suggestions.
comments: Yes, all resources were uploaded to classes v2 and were easily accessible.

Mr. Gray did an excellent job in teaching a difficult subject to students with little or no background in the topic. He has an unparalleled enthusiasm for real estate, which makes otherwise dry material fascinating and novel. I would suggest that in the future, he provide somewhat more specific instruction on the material, as I think that this would clear up some unnecessary confusion in the homework assignments.
